query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS sensor_data_ts (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  device_id INT NOT NULL,
  gateway_id INT,
  timestamp BIGINT NOT NULL,
  time_bucket BIGINT NOT NULL,
  value DECIMAL(15,6) NOT NULL,
  sensor_type VARCHAR(50),
  unit VARCHAR(20),
  quality ENUM('good', 'uncertain', 'bad') DEFAULT 'good',
  source_type ENUM('edge', 'direct', 'import') DEFAULT 'direct',
  source_id VARCHAR(50),
  INDEX idx_ts_device_time (device_id, timestamp),
  INDEX idx_ts_bucket (time_bucket),
  INDEX idx_ts_gateway (gateway_id)
)
